{"tid":2412531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傅振中批夏博義言論涉觸犯社團條例　促禁止大律師公會運作","createTime":"2021-02-18T05:41:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T08:33:33.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e7ac21248d82e4f401980f0dc06a3a81620acd09","tid":2412531,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:41:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://dw-media.wenweipo.com/dams/share/image/202102/18/602dcddce4b08a0125914f51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw-media.wenweipo.com%2Fdams%2Fshare%2Fimage%2F202102%2F18%2F602dcddce4b08a0125914f51.jpg&h=b3a7000d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://dw-media.wenweipo.com/dams/share/image/202102/18/602dcddce4b08a0125914f50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw-media.wenweipo.com%2Fdams%2Fshare%2Fimage%2F202102%2F18%2F602dcddce4b08a0125914f50.jpg&h=7f0d0093&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://dw-media.wenweipo.com/dams/share/image/202102/18/602dcddde4b08a0125914f52.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw-media.wenweipo.com%2Fdams%2Fshare%2Fimage%2F202102%2F18%2F602dcddde4b08a0125914f52.jpg&h=0c303099&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n團體「保衛香港運動」強烈譴責大律師公會企圖推卸責任，指主席言論代表公會立場，倘若公會不認同言論就應將夏博義罷免。團體主席傅振中指，夏博義被揭發前是英國民主黨黨員，其言論在社會上產生極負面的影響，令人相信他是代表英國的反華立場。<br />\n<br />\n傅振中指公會根據《社團條例》成立，該條例禁止香港的社團與外國政治聯繫，要求保安局撤查夏博義的英國政黨背景、深入調查由夏博義有份創立的「香港人權監察」與支持示威者的美國民主基金會之間的聯繫，如觸犯《社團條例》就應立即取消公會的社團註冊。團體及後高呼「英國政棍夏博義、涉觸犯社團條例；維護國家安全、取締大律師公會」等口號，並向保安局職員遞交請願信。"},{"pid":"b23f9f2bd67525707f4e66296ef7e911f6ddbbbf","tid":2412531,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"689 又批左錢啦 ?"},{"pid":"59bbe1b30d33d11ebe590294807e627d3aae65d1","tid":2412531,"uid":272677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7ac21248d82e4f401980f0dc06a3a81620acd09","tid":2412531,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T05:41:37.000Z","msg